snippet.title: Wastenauts - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A cooperative dungeon crawling RPG card game. Grab your friends and explore what’s left of the surface of Earth. Fight some machines. Blow ‘em up for parts. Put the parts back together to make cool toys. Or sell ‘em. You do you, Diver. 

Now on Kickstarter!
* Back us on Kickstarter - http://bit.ly/WastenautsKickstarter
* Join the Discord - http://bit.ly/WastenautsDiscord
* Wishlist us on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1357590
